industries 
the eec has estimated satellite television will generate 11 
billion in business for makers of reception dishes decoders other 
equipment and advertisers over the next five to seven years 
why can we not succeed where the americans were so 
successful said santer europe must put a greater effort into 
tv technology and programming 
