republic serbia and from workers angered by falling living 
standards 
ethnic serbs want changes allowing their republic one of 
yugoslavias six to have more control over the provinces of kosovo 
and vojvodina 
workers want political and economic changes because they contend 
the top party leaders are inefficent and corrupt 
