testified he used his position to gain their trust and manipulated 
their loyalty to seduce them 
last month a former explorer scout accused a cherry hills 
village patrolman of sexually abusing her in 1984 the case has not 
yet come to trial 
kephart has scheduled a youth protection workshop oct 22 for 
leaders of nearly 150 metroarea explorer scout posts 
effective last month anyone wanting to become a boy scout 
leader must submit an application that lists any drug child abuse 
or other felony charges 
scouting adminstrators also are teaching leaders to avoid being 
accused kephart said 
at one time scout leaders counseling a kid could shut the 
door and sit down to talk with him but now we tell them not to get 
alone with scouts kephart said 
in addition to the ban on oneonone contact new rules require 
that at least two supervising adults accompany outings such as 
campouts 
it is a great dilemma kephart said there are plenty of 
kids out there who really need an arm around their shoulder and 
some affection i dont really think that hugging is completely out 
but if i want to put an arm around a scout who has done well 
i do it in public and standing in the middle of the room 
