atop a pinball machine while others cheer them on 
in the new movie the accused its just another wild night 
out for the rapists and their chanting throng 
the accused which chronicles the crusade of a rape victim 
jodie foster to bring both her assaulters and their applauding 
spectators to justice shows in frank detail what rape is really 
about 
