test 
what all these women have in common says colette dowling is an 
overwhelming desire to achieve perfection in her book perfect 
women summit 1895 dowling argues that this striving for 
everhigher goals hours of aerobics every day 60hour work 
weeks making every meal from scratch is not a healthy exercise 
