disparaged culturally for eons and its a particular kind of 
gender feeling about self that gets handed down from the mother to 
the daughter 
and now that theres so much opportunity available to women i 
think weve just stepped into a new kind of performance arena i 
think were using our achievements to bolster our selfesteem in 
the way we used to use our appearance or our cooking or our 
housekeeping skills or whatever 
she cites a litany of symptoms from which these overachievers 
suffer anorexia and bulimia drug and alcohol problems compulsive 
