just providing its citizens with vacation options at a recent 
symposium on drugs development of internal tourism was cited as 
one way to discourage youth from traveling abroad and encountering 
drug users and sellers 
newspapers frequently warn readers of the travails of foreign 
travel citing examples of how unsuspecting saudis are cheated 
