in new york said it was heartbreaking that the sec was not 
extracting a financial penalty from the plotkins he said intex has 
sued the brothers for damages and compensation but said the company 
lacks the money to pursue the suit 
harry j weiss sec assistant director of enforcement said the 
plotkins were not charged with using corporate funds for their 
personal benefit but rather with failing to disclose the misuse 
he said there were no penalties possible under the charges in the 
complaint 
